main.name: HARIKRISHNAN  MOHAN
tagline: Creating websites that solve your problems
before you even know they exist.
main.shortBioPartOne: Hi, I'm Hari, a frontend developer with years of experience. I have successfully delivered products for companies and businesses worldwide, ranging from marketing websites to complex solutions.
main.shortBioPartTwo: My work emphasizes fast, elegant, and accessible user experiences, ensuring both functionality and aesthetic appeal.
main.bioPartOne: I am a passionate React Developer with over 7 years of experience in the tech industry, specializing in building scalable, high-performance web applications. My journey started in 2017 at TCS, where I initially worked as a Business Analyst, gaining deep insights into business processes and user requirements.
main.bioPartTwo: Driven by a strong interest in frontend development, I transitioned into React development during my final year at TCS. Since 2022, I have been working at CTS as a React Developer, where I focus on creating modern, efficient, and user-friendly web applications.
main.bioPartThree: With a keen eye for UI/UX, performance optimization, and state management, I take pride in delivering seamless digital experiences. My expertise extends to technologies like TypeScript, JavaScript, GraphQL, and modern frontend tooling, ensuring high-quality solutions for businesses worldwide.
main.myExpertise: My expertise lies in transforming concepts and wireframes into captivating designs that resonate with users. I leverage a diverse skill set that encompasses HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, along with various frameworks and libraries, to build responsive and interactive interfaces across multiple devices and platforms.
